                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3sb3xj6z/manifest/annotation/p2",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>will excuse the trouble this small commission will<lb/> occasion you, it being for a\n                religious purpose &amp;<lb/> required for the congregation, of which I am at present\n                the<lb/> vice president whose <del>duty</del> office is to look after these<lb/>\n                matters connected with funerals. Relying that<lb/> you will forward this small\n                commission as early<lb/> as possible &amp; awaiting your reply.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I remain Revd Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">With sentiments of the highest respect</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Your Most obdt Servant</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">\n                <hi rend=\"underline\">\n                    <persName role=\"author\">B Delvalle</persName>\n                </hi>\n            </p>\n            <p>P. S. Should you have any parcel sending to any party here<lb/> you may if you\n                please, include the above.</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3sb3xj6z/canvas/p2"
                }
              ]
